# Backend API base URL (no trailing slash). Optional in local dev if you use Vite proxy (see vite.config.js).
# If unset during dev, the app calls /api/... on the same port as Vite; Vite proxies /api to http://localhost:5000.
# For production, set this to your live API (e.g. App Runner URL).
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000
